{
  "body": "You are designing a single-screen UI mockup for a product pitch.\n\nPRODUCT BRIEF\n- App / product name: {{app_name}}\n- Screen purpose (what does this view do?): {{screen_purpose}}\n- App category: {{app_type}}\n- Target platform: {{platform}}\n\nDESIGN DIRECTION\n- Visual style: {{style}}\n- Brand accent color: {{brand_color}}\n\nDESIGN RULES\n- Use the chosen platform's native aspect (iOS Phone = 9:19.5; Android Phone = 9:20; iPad = 4:3; macOS Window = 16:10; Web Dashboard = 16:9)\n- ONE clean device frame containing ONE primary screen — no marketing chrome around it\n- All UI text must be crisp, correctly spelled, and legible (no lorem-ipsum gibberish)\n- Information hierarchy: clear primary action, secondary navigation, tertiary content\n- Real-feeling sample data (names, numbers, dates) instead of placeholders\n- Style: Dribbble shortlist / Apple Design Award polish\n- Avoid: gradient-mesh backgrounds, neon glow on every element, stock-photo avatars, fake metric charts with no axis labels, illegible micro-type\n\nIf a field is empty, infer the most useful default for the chosen app category.",
  "folderName": "Universal Briefs",
  "name": "Universal · UI Mockup",
  "parameterPreset": {
    "format": "png",
    "n": 1,
    "quality": "high",
    "size": {
      "height": 1536,
      "width": 1024
    }
  },
  "schema": "nyxtemplate",
  "tags": [
    "universal",
    "ui",
    "product",
    "mockup",
    "brief"
  ],
  "variables": [
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Forager",
      "description": "产品名",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "app_name"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Daily home feed showing personalized food picks",
      "description": "这一屏的功能（一句话）",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "screen_purpose"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "Lifestyle / Discovery",
        "Productivity / Notes",
        "Social / Messaging",
        "Finance / Banking",
        "Health / Fitness",
        "Travel / Booking",
        "E-commerce / Shopping",
        "Music / Audio",
        "AI Assistant"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "Lifestyle / Discovery",
      "description": "App 类目",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "app_type"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "iOS Phone",
        "Android Phone",
        "iPad",
        "macOS Window",
        "Web Dashboard"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "iOS Phone",
      "description": "目标平台",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "platform"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "Modern Minimal",
        "Glassmorphism",
        "Neumorphism",
        "Brutalist",
        "Material 3",
        "iOS 18 Tinted",
        "Editorial Magazine",
        "Y2K Bold",
        "Dark Premium"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "Modern Minimal",
      "description": "视觉风格",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "style"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "deep forest green",
      "description": "主色（英文颜色名最稳）",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "brand_color"
    }
  ],
  "version": 2,
  "community": {
    "author": {
      "name": "Gavin Schnee",
      "url": "https://x.com/Alaric4678"
    },
    "license": "CC-BY-4.0",
    "category": "universal"
  },
  "cover": {
    "format": "png",
    "dataBase64": ""
  }
}
